rows.label: tlk42340111_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Kisasa's favorite food is Grilled Anchortail, mo.
Eating it gives me strength, mo.

rows.label: tlk42340111_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Everyone has their favorite things, mo.
Not just food, but also musical instruments
and works of art, mo.

rows.label: tlk42340111_02_msg0003
rows.name: But the effect wears off quickly, mo.

rows.label: tlk42340111_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Kisasa stocks up on a large amount of my favorite
thing before doing my daily training, mo.

rows.label: tlk42340111_02_msg0005
rows.name:
If you're going on an adventure,
it's a good idea to stock up on a large amount
before you leave, mo.
